name: VIRTUALTRIP
tag_list: digital-branding, latin-america, south-america, argentina, branding, design, julian-bedel
overview:
VIRTUALTRIP is the first Latin American consulting company specialized in the creation and adaptation of brands for the internet.

It was founded in Buenos Aires 1998, taking an active part in the Latin American dot com boom, as partner in many startups.

After 2002, they became part of the strategic brand development consultancy FORMA Cultural Branding, changing their business model towards the creation, positioning and activation of high-end brands on the web. The company is a major player in the Latin American market.
